<br>
You or your group gets within it's agro range and just Unloads on you.  Your melee friends try to go after it but it has jboots and runs far enough to be able to nuke again.  Yet if you run away from it.. it chases you down but stays far enough not to be melee'd.  Kinda like a taste of your own medicine.<br>
<br>
Programming the mob's pathing may be complicated since if you continue running at a straight line eventually you'll reach the zone boundary where either the mob can shift to either the opposite left, opposite right, or opposite forward.  <br>
<br>
Let's say you try to trap this mob by having your melee friends wait till it hits the zone boundary and shifts to his spot where your buddies are waiting... wait, as soon as the mob feels a melee hit or root... it casts Yonder, then nukes the guy who just hit him now that he's on top of it's hate lists.  And the chase is on again.  And it so happens while chasing it, you will agro other mobs just like him now you have 2 or more of these kiting mobs to worry about... <br>
<br>
I think this would be a very interesting mob to think about for Luclin. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyofallien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>yofallien</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/2/01 4:04:27 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Mob Idea:Kiting Mob</span><hr size=1> Only hole...would be root or snare.  Nothing breaks a kite attempt like catching yourself with BoF.  (Naw I don't use AtoL's fizzles too much) To keep the principle working the Mob would have to have high MR.  I'm not sure I would welcome the change on a large scale.  But might be fun to poke around with.  Great Idea!! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaniar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aniar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/6/01 12:09:17 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Mob Idea:Kiting Mob</span><hr size=1> It'd make us a little more liked in groups I think - when he stops to nuke, so does the wizard who he's trying to kite.  Cleric follows the wizard to keep him from being stomped...  that'd be kinda like fear kiting...? <p><br>Aniar Orrenson
